%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%20game%20mods%20are%20wildly%20popular%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20it's%20easier%20than%20ever%20for%20modders%20to%20turn%20their%20hobby%20into%20a%20career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hand%20holding%20a%20video%20game%20joystick%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20a%20dollar%20sign.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862b1f53d5881a51c1c5c79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVideo%20game%20modding%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20career%20in%20game%20development%20or%20become%20a%20full-time%20independent%20job.%3Cp%3EPete%20Ryan%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVideo%20game%20modding%20has%20been%20a%20way%20for%20aspiring%20developers%20to%20land%20professional%20industry%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20creator%20economy%20has%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20modders%20to%20monetize%20the%20hobby%20independently%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-trends-fueling-great-careers-include-infrastructure-experiential-and-artificial-intelligence-2023-11%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrends%20to%20Bet%20Your%20Career%20On%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20about%20trending%20professional%20opportunities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20more%20popular%20a%20video%20game%20is%2C%20the%20more%20effort%20fans%20invest%20in%20changing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Trade%20Administration%20valued%20the%20video%20game%20industry%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trade.gov%2Fmedia-entertainment-video-games-sector%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24184%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20globally%20in%202023.%20As%20it%20continues%20to%20grow%2C%20user-created%20game%20modifications%20%E2%80%94%20more%20often%20called%20