demic%2C%20I%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20bakery%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsims-4-unlock-all-items%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Sims%204%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20had%20not%20played%20in%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20wanted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesimsresource.com%2Fmembers%2FSyboubou%2Fdownloads%2Fdetails%2Fcategory%2Fsims4-sets-objectrecolors-kitchen%2Ftitle%2Favis-kitchen-blue-mesh-not-included%2Fid%2F1488500%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20set%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20different%20color%20than%20was%20available%2C%20so%20I%20thought%20if%20I%20searched%20for%20tutorials%2C%20I%20could%20recolor%20it%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20maybe%20a%20week%20recoloring%20the%20items%2C%20and%20I%20was%20so%20proud%20of%20myself%20that%20I%20posted%20them%20on%20The%20Sims%20Resources%2C%20a%20website%20unaffiliated%20with%20The%20Sims%204%20that%20lets%20artists%20share%20custom%20content%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20posted%20it%2C%20the%20set%20has%20been%20downloaded%20more%20than%2033%2C000%20times.%20Now%2C%20I%20do%20this%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4d1ec33-d99c-429c-af43-ac458b1f49d9%5C%22%3EI%20expanded%20from%20recoloring%20to%20creating%20original%20items%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syboulette%20Deroubaix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d341e85e81483682d8db5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224232%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20trying%20her%20hand%20at%20recoloring%20a%20kitchen%20set%20for%20The%20Sims%204%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20custom%20content%20creation.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20had%20fun%20recoloring%20the%20set%2C%20I%20learned%20more%20about%203D%20modeling%20and%20texturing%2C%20and%20I%20began%20creating%20original%20items.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20I%20opened%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-patreon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatreon%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20to%20help%20me%20pay%20for%20the%20modding%20software%2C%20which%20costs%20about%20%E2%82%AC80%20a%20month.%20My%20subscriptions%20grew%2C%20and%20after%20six%20months%2C%20I%20was%20earning%20enough%20money%20to%20stop%20freelancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20was%20less%20money%20at%20first%2C%20I%20was%20completely%20free.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20clients%2C%20deadlines%2C%20or%20anyone%20to%20tell%20me%20what%20to%20do.%20I%20kept%20a%20few%20freelance%20jobs%20during%20the%20transition%2C%20but%20after%20a%20year%20or%20so%2C%20I%20was%20earning%20more%20than%20I%20did%20in%20my%20advertising%20job%2C%20so%20I%20thought%2C%20%3Cem%3EI'm%20never%20going%20back%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20now%20make%20more%20than%20I%20did%20in%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ecbd5c9-f1f3-4fef-a73f-4a835ee5fba5%5C%22%3EMy%20work%20schedule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syboulette%20Deroubaix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d348c3d5881a51c1cdf18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeroubaix%20said%20modular%20items%2C%20such%20as%20kitchen%20counters%2C%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20items%20to%20create%20in%20The%20Sims%204.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20four%20years%20now.%20Every%20month%20on%20my%20Patreon%2C%20I%20post%20a%20set%2C%20which%20includes%2020%20to%2030%20items%20inspired%20by%20a%20theme%20or%20room.%20All%20of%20my%20subscribers%20get%20early%20access%20to%20my%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20by%20making%20a%20mood%20board%20and%20looking%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-add-notes-on-pinterest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPinterest%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Google%20for%20anything%20that%20inspires%20me.%20Once%20I've%20gathered%20references%2C%20I'll%20pick%20a%20number%20of%20items%20to%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20spread%20my%20work%20throughout%20the%20month.%20I%20can%20create%20one%20item%20in%20five%20to%20eight%20hours%2C%20so%20I%20usually%20make%20one%20per%20day.%20Then%2C%20I%20test%20every%20item%20in%20the%20game%20and%20take%20screenshots%20to%20show%20my%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a6a11bb-5af3-4088-aa20-fda4ad8907a6%5C%22%3EHow%20I%20make%20money%20as%20a%20modder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222050%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syboulette%20Deroubaix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d33723d5881a51c1cdead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHer%20Creator%20Kit%2C%20an%20official%20content%20pack%20she%20developed%20in%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Sims%2C%20was%20released%20this%20April.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20games%20endorse%20monetized%20mods.%20The%20Sims%204%20modders%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20officially%20sell%20their%20creations%2C%20but%20The%20Sims%20allows%20modders%20to%20release%20content%20for%20free%20with%20monetized%20early%20access.%20This%20means%20people%20who%20subscribe%20to%20my%20Patreon%20get%20my%20items%20three%20weeks%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20then%20my%20custom%20content%20becomes%20free%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%2C%20I%20only%20had%20Patreon%20and%20The%20Sims%20Resource%2C%20which%20pays%20featured%20artists.%20After%20a%20year%2C%20I%20created%20my%20own%20website%20with%20ads%2C%20which%20also%20created%20some%20income.%20Patreon%20is%20still%20my%20biggest%20source%20of%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOccasionally%2C%20I'll%20have%20an%20opportunity%20from%20an%20outside%20company%2C%20like%20the%20collaboration%20I%20did%20last%20year%20with%20The%20Sims%20for%20my%20official%20Creator%20Kit.%20The%20Sims%20also%20collaborated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-stay-home-kids-side-hustle-makes-more-money-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECurseForge%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20create%20an%20official%20platform%20for%20custom%20content%2C%20and%20I%20earn%20income%20from%20that%20website%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a80a1d2-2424-4e10-b9f5-8a26eb30e458%5C%22%3EThe%20challenges%20and%20rewards%20of%20modding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226855%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syboulette%20Deroubaix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d339e85e81483682d8d80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20her%20latest%20custom%20content%20releases%20is%20the%20Splash%20%26amp%3B%20Sass%20set%2C%20which%20includes%20brightly-colored%20pool%20decor.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20learning%20curve%20to%20modding%20was%20very%20steep%20in%20the%20beginning.%20I%20taught%20myself%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fgame-development-courses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20design%20software%20like%20Blender%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fadobe-creative-cloud-photoshop-premiere-pro-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdobe%20Substance%203D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20modify%20more%20difficult%20items%2C%20but%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20became%20a%20more%20public%20figure%20as%20a%20Sims%204%20modder%20by%20sharing%20on%20social%20media%20and%20streaming%20on%20Twitch.%20Some%20players%20have%20negative%20opinions%20about%20my%20job%2C%20and%20some%20pirate%20my%20creations%2C%20but%20this%20comes%20with%20any%20creative%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20the%20perfect%20job%20because%20I%20don't%20rely%20on%20anyone.%20Even%20though%20I%20have%20a%20suggestion%20channel%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-discord%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiscord%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20fans%20can%20suggest%20ideas%2C%20I%20can%20do%20whatever%20I%20want.%20It's%20full%20creative%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20more%20creative%20than%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20in%20advertising.%20It's%20so%20nice%20to%20have%20people%20playing%20with%20your%20creations%20and%20sending%20you%20screenshots%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BLook%20what%20I%20made%20with%20your%20set.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ce5f6bc-7e9a-4e26-8e85-07951b02edaa%5C%22%3EMy%20advice%20to%20aspiring%20modders%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Syboulette%20Deroubaix%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d33d73d5881a51c1cded6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeroubaix%20said%20connecting%20with%20the%20community%20is%20important%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20start%20modding%20video%20games.%3Cp%3EMathilde%20Lagarrigue%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20making%20a%20beautiful%20thing%20is%20not%20enough.%20Communication%20is%20very%20important.%20Be%20on%20every%20social%20media%20and%20try%20to%20reach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-jobs-creator-influencer-hiring-trends-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%20creators%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20YouTube%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgui