ers%20for%20apps%20from%20Flex%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-uber-upfront-pricing-could-be-key-to-business-turnaround-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Instacart%20often%20say%20that%20the%20flexibility%20to%20work%20when%20they%20want%20is%20a%20major%20reason%20that%20they%20opt%20to%20earn%20money%20as%20independent%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flex%20drivers'%20experience%20is%20one%20example%20of%20how%20gig%20work%20may%20not%20be%20as%20flexible%20in%20practice%20as%20some%20workers%20expect.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriving-for-uber-lyft-flexibility-gig-work-doordash-stock-earnings-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERide-hailing%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20tend%20to%20find%20that%20demand%20for%20their%20services%20is%20higher%20during%20certain%20times%20of%20the%20day%20or%20days%20of%20the%20week%2C%20and%20those%20times%20may%20or%20may%20not%20align%20with%20their%20own%20availability.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20may%20have%20to%20work%20outside%20their%20preferred%20hours%20or%20earn%20less%20than%20they%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Flex%20driver%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20whom%20Pinto%20interviewed%20for%20the%20study%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20she%20frequently%20checks%20Flex%20when%20she's%20not%20working%20to%20try%20to%20claim%20shifts%20that%20pay%20around%20%2430%20an%20hour.%20That's%20good%20pay%20in%20her%20area%2C%20she%20said%3A%20Other%20shifts%20pay%20closer%20to%20%2420%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Reddit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FAmazonFlexDrivers%2Fcomments%2F1gf7r1q%2Fnew_amazon_driver_when_do_new_blocks_drop%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20posters%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20say%20that%20they%20are%20Amazon%20Flex%20drivers%20give%20advice%20to%20new%20drivers%20on%20how%20to%20claim%20work.%20Among%20their%20tips%3A%20Figure%20out%20when%20shifts%20drop%20in%20your%20area%20and%20be%20ready%20to%20claim%20them%20the%20moment%20they're%20available%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20that's%20early%20in%20the%20morning.%20Some%20have%20also%20complained%20about%20issues%20with%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20BI%20spoke%20with%20said%20that%20she%20has%20sometimes%20been%20locked%20out%20of%20the%20app%20after%20working%20shifts%20for%20Flex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20lockouts%20weren't%20consistent%2C%20though%2C%20and%20she%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20caused%20them.%20The%20driver%20said%20she%20was%20able%20to%20claim%20more%20than%20five%20hours%20of%20work%20a%20day%20for%20this%20week%2C%20when%20Amazon%20is%20offering%20four%20days%20of%20sales%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fbest-amazon-prime-day-deals-live-updates-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrime%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Amazon%20allows%20Flex%20workers%20to%20claim%20shifts%20up%20to%20a%20few%20days%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e6a5e61-6957-4007-a775-76e6cb158f09%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Flex%20is%20one%20part%20of%20the%20expanding%20world%20of%20gig%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENELP's%20report%20points%20to%20other%20conditions%20that%20Flex%20workers%20face%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20measures%20workers'%20productivity%20using%20several%20metrics%2C%20such%20as%20the%20percentage%20of%20packages%20they%20deliver%20on%20a%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20of%20those%20performance%20metrics%20are%20always%20within%20a%20Flex%20driver's%20control%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20%26quot%3BLong%20queues%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20parking%20at%20a%20delivery%20station%20or%20a%20glitching%20Global%20Positioning%20System%20on%20a%20driver's%20smartphone%20can%20negatively%20affect%20'on-time%20arrival%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20reads%2C%20referring%20to%20another%20metric%20Amazon%20uses%20to%20evaluate%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20uses%20metrics%20like%20on-time%20arrival%20to%20determine%20a%20driver's%20%26quot%3Bstanding%26quot%3B%20grade.%20The%20grade%20can%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20affect%20a%20driver's%20pay%20and%20access%20to%20future%20shifts%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20told%20BI%20that%20standing%20doesn't%20affect%20how%20much%20work%20a%20Flex%20driver%20can%20sign%20up%20for%2C%20and%20that%20grade%20accounts%20for%20circumstances%20outside%20a%20driver's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20report's%20conclusions%20is%20that%20Flex%20drivers%20are%20misclassified%20as%20independent%20contractors.%20It%20says%20they%20should%20be%20considered%20employees%20since%20Amazon's%20control%20of%20their%20working%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20through%20metric-based%20standing%2C%20means%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bare%20not%20truly%20in%20business%20for%20themselves%20like%20legitimate%20independent%20contractors%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGig%20workers%20are%20generally%20classified%20as%20independent%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%C2%A0gig%20work%20continues%20to%20expand.%20Retailers%20like%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWalmart%20and%20Target%20also%20have%20their%20own%20gig%20workforces%20picking%20up%20and%20delivering%20customers'%20orders.%20Apps%20that%20bring%20gig%20work%20to%20other%20industries%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-for-nursing-apps-show-issues-across-expanding-gig-economy-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enursing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20also%20proliferated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20it%20being%20used%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20corporations%20and%20different%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20Pinto%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20gig%20work%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C