20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%2C%20and%20a%20soda.%20The%20food%20was%20served%20on%20a%20stadium-style%20paper%20tray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20was%20tasty.%20I%20paid%20%243%20for%20the%20soda%2C%20%247.50%20for%20the%20mac%20'n%20cheese%2C%20and%20%243.50%20for%20the%20cookie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first-class%20meal%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20brownie%20dessert.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dessert%20Amtrak%20first%20class%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862e91c3d5881a51c1c63a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20brownie%20was%20fudgy%20and%20topped%20with%20airy%20whipped%20cream.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first-class%20dining%20car%2C%20we%20were%20brought%20brownies%20after%20the%20dinner%20service.%20The%20brownies%20were%20hot%20and%20fudgy%20and%20topped%20with%20chocolate%20syrup%20and%20airy%20whipped%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20coach%20bathroom%20was%20significantly%20more%20spacious%20than%20an%20airplane%20bathroom.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22amtrak%20coach%20bathroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862ec92f748d8c055f4ac02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20economy-class%20bathroom%20was%20spacious%20and%20decently%20clean.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20economy%20bathroom%20was%20spacious%20compared%20to%20airplane%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20it%20was%20also%20ADA-accessible.%20Although%20it%20still%20felt%20like%20a%20public%20bathroom%2C%20it%20was%20decently%20clean%20after%20the%20nearly%20six-hour%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlthough%20private%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20train%2C%20the%20first-class%20bathroom%20was%20a%20little%20awkward%2C%20especially%20for%20two%20people.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bathroom%20amtrak%20roomette%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862eee33d5881a51c1c64a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first-class%20roomette%20has%20its%20own%20private%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20roomette%2C%20which%20had%20its%20own%20bathroom%2C%20a%20toilet%20and%20a%20sink%20opened%20from%20the%20stairs%20going%20up%20to%20the%20upper%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20room%20door%20and%20curtains%20were%20closed%2C%20it%20was%20very%20private%20for%20me%20as%20a%20solo%20traveler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20two%20people%20in%20the%20roomette%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20little%20too%20awkward%2C%20as%20it's%20not%20at%20all%20separated%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20roomette%20offered%20a%20better%2C%20fuller%2C%20and%20more%20comfortable%20experience%2C%20and%20I%20would%20book%20it%20again.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22author%20with%20sleeping%20space%20in%20amtrak%20roomette%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d784285e81483682d97c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20long-distance%20travel%2C%20I'd%20choose%20the%20roomette%20over%20the%20coach%2C%20although%20the%20economy%20option%20is%20good%20for%20short%20distances.%3Cp%3EKristine%20Villarroel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20enjoyed%20both%20experiences%2C%20the%20roomette%20offered%20a%20fuller%20experience%20that%20was%20different%20from%20what%20you%20could%20get%20through%20plane%20or%20bus%20travel%2C%20whereas%20the%20coach%20option%20felt%20similar%20to%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20at