0a%20half.%20That%20would%20still%20be%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20competitors%20like%20YouTube%2C%20which%20gets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Fyoutube-shorts-200-billion-daily-views%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20billions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20video%20views%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20X%20has%20a%20bespoke%20catalog%20of%20shows%2C%20its%20pitch%20to%20creators%20is%20closer%20to%20YouTube%20than%20streamers%20like%20Netflix.%20X%20is%20not%20throwing%20any%20development%20money%20to%20shows%20branded%20as%20originals%20or%20buying%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it's%20pitching%20creators%20on%20monetizing%20their%20videos%20through%20X%20Amplify%2C%20its%20video%20ad%20sales%20tool%2C%20and%20offering%20to%20build%20custom%20ad%20treatments%20for%20shows.%20The%20creator%20gets%20a%20certain%20percentage%20of%20the%20ad%20revenue%20based%20on%20specific%20contract%20negotiations.%20Unlike%20YouTube%2C%20X%20doesn't%20have%20a%20standard%20rate.%20X%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222454%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Serena%20Williams%20is%20congratulated%20by%20her%20sister%20and%20opponent%20Venus%20Williams%20following%20their%20ladies'%20singles%20third-round%20match%20on%20Day%20Five%20of%20the%202018%20US%20Open.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65650f14fe5bc6545ebcaf69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221908%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVenus%20Williams%20(left)%20and%20Serena%20Williams%20are%20launching%20a%20show%20on%20X.%3Cp%3EJulian%20Finney%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f19b7a29-f9f9-4ff3-a496-7132b6cc3105%5C%22%3EX%20is%20pitching%20culture%2C%20not%20politics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20one%20of%20X's%20selling%20points%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20build%20series%20around%20newsmaking%20moments.%20It's%20starting%20to%20build%20shows%20tied%20to%20creators%20around%20big%20events%20like%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20inherently%20social%20platform%20that%20now%20has%20a%20great%20video%20viewing%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20because%20it's%20the%20first%20place%20people%20check%2C%20it's%20really%20the%20one%20platform%20that%20truly%20moves%20at%20the%20velocity%20of%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20X%2C%20video%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20boost%20user%20engagement%20while%20moving%20the%20platform%20toward%20sports%20and%20lifestyle%20content%20and%20away%20from%20hot-button%20political%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20to%20work%20with%20strong%20creators%2C%20whether%20that's%20endemic%20creators%2C%20athletes%2C%20musicians%2C%20actors%2C%20or%20even%20sports%20teams%20in%20leagues%2C%20in%20the%20most%20highly%20engaged%20content%20categories%20on%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20next%2C%20Smith%20said%20he's%20pursuing%20more%20projects%20with%20the%20NFL.%20He's%20also%20looking%20for%20more%20finance-focused%20shows%20in%20the%20vein%20of%20Anthony%20Pompliano's%20daily%20business%20show%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20Desk%20of%20Anthony%20Pompliano%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20female-aimed%20fare%20like%20Khlo%C3%A9%20Kardashian's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fi%2Fevents%2F1875987636159905792%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhlo%C3%A9%20in%20Wonderland%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20podcast%20and%20Alexis%20Ohanian-produced%20%26quot%3BThe%20Offseason%26quot%3B%20about%20women's%20soccer.%20(Ohanian%20is%20married%20to%20Serena%20Williams).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20categories%2C%20Smith%20has%20ambitions%20for%20series%20that%20take%20viewers%20behind%20the%20scenes%20with%20music%20artists%20and%20gamers%2C%20and%20competition%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20love%20to%20crack%20a%20daily%20game%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223db785fc-4636-4984-ac8c-71162dc3a6ca%5C%22%3EX%20faces%20some%20skepticism%20about%20its%20video%20plans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EX%20still%20needs%20to%20convince%20more%20producers%20and%20advertisers%20that%20it's%20a%20worthwhile%20destination%20for%20their%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Smith's%20former%20boss%2C%20Brett%20Weitz%2C%20left%20in%20April%20after%20about%20two%20years%20as%20X's%20global%20head%20of%20content%2C%20talent%2C%20and%20brand%20sales%20and%20wasn't%20replaced%2C%20some%20in%20the%20industry%20wondered%20about%20the%20platform's%20commitment%20in%20that%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20entertainment%20exec%20who%20recently%20heard%20X's%20originals%20pitch%20said%20it%20seemed%20to%20still%20be%20in%20the%20experimental%20phase%20and%20questioned%20whether%20brands%20would%20be%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20confident%20I%20could%20get%20enough%20views%20and%20monetize%20it%20with%20a%20brand%20that's%20comfortable%20being%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20brands%20aren't%20as%20confident%20in%20what%20the%20value%20of%20the%20views%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20advertisers%20fled%20X%20after%20Musk%20acquired%20the%20platform%20in%20October%202022%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20some%20recent%20signs%20that%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-advertising-spending-data-analysis-mixed-recovery-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ead%20revenue%20is%20turning%20around%3C%2Fa%3E.%20X%20also%20sued%20several%20major%20brands%2C%20alleging%20they%20illegally%20withheld%20ad%20dollars%20from%20the%20platform.%20The%20environment%20around%20X%20can%20make%20it%20a%20tough%20sell%20for%20some%20advertisers%20and%20producers%20when%20there%20are%20bigger%20platforms%20without%20the%20polarizing%20history%2C%20such%20as%20YouTube.%20Some%20partners%20also%20prefer%20more%20templated%20offerings%20that%20they%20can%20slot%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegarding%20past%20controversy%2C%20Smith%20countered%20that%20the%20platform%20has%20been%20able%20to%20attract%20big%20names%20like%20the%20Williamses%20and%20Kardashian%2C%20and%20rolled%20out%20improvements%20for%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20great%20things%20about%20original%20programming%20is%20that%20it%20shows%20the%20innovation%20of%20the%20platform%2C%20the%20video%20offering%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20very%20dynamic%20offering%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20actual%20types%20of%20ad%20units%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20one%20size%20fits%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-original-video-expansion-plans-serena-williams-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752060901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d375085e81483682d8e4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-original-video-expansion-plans-serena-williams-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22X%20has%20trailed%20other%20platforms%20in%20video%2C%20but%20Mitchell%20Smith%2C%20head%20of%20original%20content%20at%20X%2C%20wants%20Hollywood%20to%20know%20it's%20open%20for%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-original-video-expansion-plans-serena-williams-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Girls%20Told%20To%20Strip%20For%20Period%20Check%20After%20Blood%20Stains%20Found%20In%20School%20Bathroom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Girls%20in%20a%20Maharashtra%20school%2C%20between%20classes%205-10%2C%20were%20forced%20to%20strip%20and%20examined%20by%20teachers%20after%20blood%20stains%20were%20found%20