%20be%20%26quot%3Bprocessing%26quot%3B%20(a%20word%20Barry%20now%20abhors)%2C%20and%20he'd%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BDoes%20everything%20always%20have%20to%20be%20a%20workshop%20around%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20(I'd%20remind%20him%2C%20though%2C%20that%20we%20did%20meet%20in%20a%20workshop%2C%20after%20all!)%20So%2C%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20compromise%2C%20we've%20developed%20what%20we%20call%20our%20%26quot%3Bstatute%20of%20limitations%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20a%20point%20when%20we%20agree%20to%20no%20longer%20bring%20up%20a%20past%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20we%20don't%20try%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-marriage-lessons-conflict-healthy-space-good-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresolve%20conflicts%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20one%20of%20us%20does%20something%20that%20bothers%20the%20other.%20But%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20conversations%2C%20assuming%20we've%20reached%20a%20resolution%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it's%20not%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20then%20the%20subject%20is%20closed.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20it's%20no%20longer%20%26quot%3Bour%26quot%3B%20problem%3B%20it's%20his%20problem%20or%20mine%2C%20to%20handle%20independently%3A%20discuss%20it%20with%20a%20friend%2C%20write%20about%20it%2C%20or%20otherwise%20sort%20it%20out%20on%20our%20own%20without%20involving%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220af7fe27-94ee-4395-8f9b-f7f99e7eb1dd%5C%22%3EOur%20system%20works%20for%20us%2C%20even%20if%20we%20do%20screw%20up%20occasionally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20we%20sometimes%20screw%20up.%20One%20of%20us%20occasionally%20does%20play%20tit-for-tat%2C%20or%20brings%20up%20something%20that%20we%20have%20closed%20the%20book%20on.%20If%20we%20do%2C%20the%20other%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20remember%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20agreements%20didn't%20arrive%20preserved%2C%20polished%2C%20and%20ready-made.%20Hardly!%20They%20evolved%20gradually%2C%20over%20years%20and%20years%20of%20practice%2C%20disagreements%2C%20difficult%20conversations%2C%20therapy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychedelics-key-long-happy-marriage-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsychedelics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20what%20we%20call%20%26quot%3Bour%20dome%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20safe%20place%20where%20we%20share%20with%20deep%20honesty%20something%20that%20is%20troubling%20us%20about%20the%20other.%20Hammering%20out%20our%20ground%20rules%20along%20the%20winding%20road%20of%20our%20marriage%20is%20part%20of%20what%20made%20us%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20have%20given%20us%20a%20deep%20foundation%20of%20trust.%20Without%20them%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20feel%20safe%20with%20each%20other%2C%20enjoy%20our%20lives%20as%20fully%2C%20or%20have%20so%20much%20fun%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuite%20simply%2C%20without%20these%20ground%20rules%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20who%20we%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeys-success-long-happy-51-year-marriage-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752055621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686bfae0f748d8c055f51357%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeys-success-long-happy-51-year-marriage-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20Barry%20and%20I%20have%20been%20together%20for%2051%20years.%20We%20spend%20a%20month%20apart%20every%20year%20and%20we%20don't%20keep%20score.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22louisarogers51%40gmail.com%20(Louisa%20Rogers)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeys-success-long-happy-51-year-marriage-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20cuts%20visa%20validity%20for%20most%20Nigerian%20applicants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%2