p%3EOn%20the%20rare%20occasions%20when%20we%20did%20run%20into%20a%20resident%20in%20the%20elevator%20or%20garage%2C%20the%20conversation%20was%20typically%20short.%20They'd%20ask%20where%20we%20were%20from%2C%20if%20we%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-now-good-time-to-buy-home-real-estate-agents-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehad%20a%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20(we%20don't)%2C%20and%20then%20it%20would%20end%20with%20them%20usually%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20welcome.%26quot%3B%20No%20invitation%20to%20meet%20up%20later%20or%20neighborly%20gesture%2C%20like%20to%20come%20by%20if%20we%20ever%20needed%20a%20cup%20of%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20exception%20was%20one%20lovely%20woman%20from%20our%20complex%20%E2%80%94%20she%20did%20invite%20us%20out%20to%20coffee%20with%20our%20immediate%20neighbors%20next%20door%2C%20who%20are%20friends%20of%20hers.%20Everyone%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20good%20time%2C%20and%20I%20hoped%20it%20would%20become%20a%20regular%20thing%2C%20but%20it%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2016%20months%20since%20then%2C%20we've%20had%20coffee%20with%20the%20lovely%20woman%20once%20(we%20invited%20her).%20And%20the%20neighbors'%20subsequent%20perfunctory%20interactions%20indicated%20that%20they%20weren't%20interested%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffling-relationship-neighbor-breakup-awkward-moved-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eneighborly%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20still%20feels%20odd%20to%20know%20that%20people%20with%20whom%20we%20share%20a%20wall%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20ones%20we'd%20call%20on%20if%20we%20needed%20to%20borrow%20an%20egg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20residents%20have%20actually%20described%20the%20feel%20of%20our%20complex%20as%20%26quot%3Binsular%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20we%20know%20we're%20not%20imagining%20things.%20Many%20residents%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-home-regret-too-much-house-mistakes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecond%20or%20third%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20this%20is%20just%20a%20place%20to%20roost%20temporarily%2C%20not%20a%20place%20where%20they%20want%20to%20put%20down%20roots%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20building%20or%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207e7c942-c14b-4ae0-b526-9f06d4dc7214%5C%22%3EOur%20condo%20isn't%20the%20only%20place%20that%20feels%20insular%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22St.%20Petersburg%2C%20Florida%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686bf768f748d8c055f512ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESt.%20Petersburg%2C%20Florida%2C%20has%20a%20population%20of%20about%20250%2C000.%3Cp%3Epeeterv%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20St.%20Petersburg%20neighborhood%2C%20we%20exchanged%20house%20keys%2C%20traded%20tools%20and%20plants%2C%20and%20were%20happy%20to%20feed%20pets%20or%20check%20on%20the%20pool%20for%20neighbors%20who%20were%20out%20of%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20place%20where%20we%20helped%20out%20with%20a%20bouncy%20house%20birthday%20party%20and%20shared%20front%20yard%20cocktails%20while%20the%20street%20was%20swarmed%20with%20trick-or-treaters.%20Despite%20having%20a%20population%20of%20250%2C000%2C%20St.%20Pete%20had%20a%20small-town%20feel%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnnapolis%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%2040%2C000%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20feels%20quite%20different.%20Several%20locals%20have%20even%20told%20us%20that%20Annapolis%20itself%20isn't%20that%20friendly%20to%20newcomers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20you%20have%20to%20live%20here%20for%2030%20years%20before%20you're%20accepted.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20joking%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20Still%2C%20our%20experience%20hasn't%20been%20too%20far%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ce5038c-490a-47bb-aee2-b448e06f7b6e%5C%22%3EWe%20got%20most%20of%20what%20we%20wanted%2C%20but%20aren't%20positive%20it%20was%20the%20right%20move%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20what%20we%20wanted%20from%20our%20new%20home%2C%20we're%20three%20for%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20several%20sailing%20clubs%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20we're%20involved%20with%20theatre%20and%20arts%20initiatives%2C%20and%20we've%20enjoyed%20some%20St.%20Johns%20College%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20to%20buy%20a%20winter%20coat%20and%20deal%20with%20snowy%2C%20unplowed%20streets%20was%20definitely%20not%20part%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20but%20we've%20adjusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20disappointing%20surprise%20is%20having%20to%20accept%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20building%20we%20live%20in%20is%20simply%20where%20we%20lay%20our%20heads%20and%20collect%20our%20mail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we've%20identified%20a%20handful%20of%20friendly%20condo%20dwellers%20in%20the%2017%20months%20since%20we%20moved%20in%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20seem%20committed%20to%20maintaining%20a%20sense%20of%20privacy%20over%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20that%20community%20we%20valued%20has%20required%20much%20more%20time%20and%20effort%20on%20our%20part%20than%20it%20did%20in%20St.%20Pete%2C%20but%20we're%20trying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20whether%20the%20condo%20or%20the%20city%20was%20the%20wrong%20move%2C%20the%20jury%20is%20still%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-florida-to-maryland-hardest-thing-making-friends-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752053401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686bf68485e81483682d798b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-florida-to-maryland-hardest-thing-making-friends-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mary%20Ellen%20Collins%20moved%20