n%20of%20the%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20involved%20repurposing%20the%20Burma%20Teak%20that%20was%20found%20under%20the%20plaster%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030%20months%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpainstaking%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20were%20directed%20towards%20retaining%20existing%20details%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20in%20a%20more%20nuanced%20fashion.%20Malik%20adds%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etouches%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0were%20included%20in%20every%20way%20possible.%20For%20months%2C%20the%20team%20scraped%20away%20at%20old%20plaster%2C%20which%20yielded%20brickwork%20and%20vintage%20Burma%20teak%20woodwork%20underneath.%20Look%20around%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20in%20some%20places%20the%20colours%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20match.%20Malik%20underscores%20that%20no%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20polish%20the%20teak%20wood%20surfaces.%20This%20lends%20a%20rugged%2C%20raw%20touch%20to%20the%20staircase%20at%20the%20Native%20Restaurant%20and%20Bar%2C%20its%20roof%20structure%20and%20flooring%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ice%20Factory%20roof%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20if%20there%20are%20mismatches%3F%20It%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20space%2C%20the%20architect%20believes.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20in%20places%20where%20it%20was%20necessitated%2C%20safety%20upgrades%20were%20made.%20These%20include%20structural%20reinforcements%20to%20the%20walls%20and%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20that%20took%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20was%20the%20main%20Ice%20Factory%2C%20sub-station%2C%20cold%20storage%2C%20and%20the%20ice-cubing%20area.%20