0Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20should%20visit%20my%20orchard%20to%20see%20the%20tree%20and%20understand%20the%20variety%20of%20mangoes%2C%20each%20with%20its%20distinct%20qualities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20proudly%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20life%20around%20mangoes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20approach%20to%20grafting%20has%20earned%20him%20national%20and%20international%20recognition.%20This%20ancient%20technique%2C%20which%20involves%20joining%20a%20branch%20from%20one%20tree%20to%20the%20rootstock%20of%20another%2C%20has%20been%20used%20in%20agriculture%20for%20centuries.%20Through%20his%20research%20and%20years%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20he%20has%20created%20a%20mango%20tree%20that%20bears%20a%20staggering%20350%20varieties%20of%20mangoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-04-at-19.23.45-1-1743785875.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kalimullah%20Khan%20has%20created%20a%20mango%20tree%20that%20bears%20350%20varieties%20of%20mangoes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-04-at-19.23.45-1-1743785875.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-04-at-19.23.45-1-1743785875-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-04-at-19.23.45-1-1743785875-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-04-at-19.23.45-1-1743785875-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-04-at-19.23.45-1-1743785875-1200x900.jpeg%20