20the%20cocoa%20farms%20of%20West%20Godavari%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Belgian%20nor%20Swiss%2C%20this%20chocolate%20is%20proudly%20and%20entirely%20Indian.%20With%20over%20300%20products%20across%2050%20categories%2C%20Manam%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262803%2Fmumbai-woman-entrepreneur-healthy-snacks-oats-flax-seeds-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChocolate%20is%20redefining%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20perception%20of%20Indian-origin%20cocoa%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%20And%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20it%20is%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20craft%2C%20community%2C%20and%20cocoa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2015%2C%202023%2C%20Manam%20Chocolate%20launched%20its%20first%20collection%20in%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Banjara%20Hills%20%E2%80%94%20a%20proud%20tribute%20to%20the%20farmers%20who%20made%20it%20all%20possible.%20Among%20its%20most%20celebrated%20offerings%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3EManam%20Signature%20Tablet%3C%2Fem%3E%20collection%2C%20featuring%2043%20unique%20bars.%20Two%20of%20these%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EFarm%20Tablet%20No.1%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ENo.3%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20made%20from%20beans%20grown%20by%20farmers%20D%20Hari%20Krishna%20and%20GVS%20Prasad%2C%20each%20bar%20carrying%20the%20distinct%20flavour%20of%20a%20single%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Farm%20to%20Tablet%3A%20A%20Story%20of%20Trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Single%20Farmer%20Series%20recognises%20farms%20that%20have%20unique%20flavour%20profiles.%20The%20craft%20chocolate%20is%20about%20complexity%20and%20flavour.%20Everything%20we%20do%20is%20to%20derive%20complexity%20from%20the%20bean%20without%20adding%20anything.%20So%20these%20two%20or%20three%20farms%20we%20have%20identified%20as%20being%20interested%20enough%20in%20the%20single-farmer%20series%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaitanya%20Muppala%2C%20CEO%20of%20Distinct%20O