0with%20Almond%20House.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20brand%20that%20my%20father%20ran%3B%20now%20it%20has%2014%20stores%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Chaitanya%20Muppala.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20my%20career%20started%20in%202013%20with%20Almond%20House.%20We%20identified%20the%20strategies%2C%20and%20we%20grew%20that%20out%20into%20a%20fairly%20large%20business%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20brand%20that%20my%20father%20ran%3B%20now%20it%20has%2014%20stores%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2035-year-old%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%205000%20square%20feet%20of%20space%2C%20Almond%20House%20employs%20various%20strategies.%20The%20%E2%80%98House%20of%20Brands%E2%80%99%20is%20one%20among%20them.%20They%20operate%20multiple%20brands%20under%20one%20roof%20under%20this%20strategy.%20They%20have%20a%20%E2%80%98Chat%E2%80%99%20brand%20called%20Gappe%20Vappe%20and%20an%20ultra-natural%20gelato%20brand%20called%20Indulge%20Ice%20Cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20have%20a%20quarter%20of%20their%20business%20dedicated%20to%20corporate%20gifting.%20Customers%20visiting%20this%20segment%20would%20request%20gift%20items%20related%20to%20chocolate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20politely%20decline%20their%20request%20since%20chocolate%20items%20weren%E2%80%99t%20available.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20anything%20about%20chocolate%20at%20that%20time%20because%20chocolate%20was%20always%20something%20that%20we%20bought%20from%20a%20supplier%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Muppala.%20However%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20branching%20out%20into%20the%20chocolate%20market%20sparked%20his%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-500x333.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772.jpg%201650w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMuppala%20study%20found%20a%20key%20understanding%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20chocolate%20inherently%20depends%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20started%20mapping%20and%20contextualizing%20the%20market%20to%20understand%20what%20chocolate%20is.%20%E2%80%9CI%20quickly%20realized%20that%20anybody%20involved%20in%20the%20chocolate%20industry%20in%20India%20is%20buying%20chocolate%2C%20melting%20it%2C%20moulding%20it%2C%20adding%20nuts%2C%20flavour%2C%20and%20sea%20salt%2C%20and%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F217619%2Fdark-chocolate-health-benefits-reduced-heart-risk-improved-brain-function-buy-online-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%3Epackaging%20it%20as%20their%20own%20chocolate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20enough%20sustainable%20differentiation%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hyderabad-based%20entrepreneur%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Almond%20House%2C%20he%20understood%20that%20mithai%20is%20regional.%20Every%20region%20has%20different%20preferences.%20I%20started%20realizing%20that%20our%20younger%20people%E2%80%99s%20moods%20are%20shifting%20from%20traditional%20categories%20like%20mithai%20to%20contemporary%20modern%20and%2C%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20Western%20categories%20like%20patisserie%20chocolates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20every%20city%20has%20two%20or%20three%20chocolate%20brands%20like%20his%20mithai%20brands%2C%20but%20if%20they%20all%20source%20the%20same%20ingredients%20from%20the%20same%20multinational%20supplier%2C%20the%20end%20product%20will%20be%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELiving%20with%20Farmers%2C%20Learning%20from%20the%20Soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20the%20art%20of%20chocolate%20making%2C%20small-batch%20chocolate%20production%2C%20and%20the%20principles%20of%20craft%20chocolate%2C%20his%20study%20found%20a%20key%20understanding%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20chocolate%20inherently%20depends%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20prompted%20him%20to%20search%20further%20about%20the%20origin%20of%20beans%2C%20and%20that%20led%20him%20to%20farms%20in%202018%2C%20where%20he%20spent%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20with%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20West%20Godavari%20district%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20the%20farmers%20were%20skeptical.%20They%20viewed%20me%20as%20an%20outsider%20from%20the%20city%20doing%20something%20new.%20I%20lived%20among%20them%20to%20win%20their%20trust.%20It%20took%20two%20to%20three%20years%20to%20build%20their%20confidence%20in%20me.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20business%20with%20them%20and%20help%20them%20make%20more%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20businessperson%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-1024x1536.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-150x225.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747.jpg%201083w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGVS%20Prasad%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20Manam%20Chocolate%20gives%20us%20pride%20to%20see%20how%20this%20fruit%20of%20our%20land%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20something%20so%20delightful.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20main%20goal%20was%20to%20empower%20farmers.%20I%20ensured%20that%20farmers%20profit%20more%20and%20also%20improve%20our%20revenue%20distribution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGVS%20Prasad%20(Guduri%20Venkata%20Sivarama%20Prasad)%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20growing%20cocoa%20since%20the%20mid-1960s%2C%20but%20working%20with%20Manam%20Chocolate%20gives%20us%20tremendous%20pride%20to%20see%20how%20this%20fruit%20of%20our%20land%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20something%20so%20delightful.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevarapalli%20Hari%20Krishna%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20Manam%20Chocolate%20and%20DOPL%2C%20we%20are%20not%20treated%20like%20suppliers%20but%20as%20partners%2C%20even%20co-creators.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20used%20to%20grow%20cocoa%20without%20really%20knowing%20how%20much%20impact%20the%20soil%2C%20the%20climate%2C%20or%20our%20handling%20could%20have%20on%20the%20flavour%20of%20the%20cocoa%20beans.%20The%20engagement%20has%20enhanced%20our%20understanding%20that%20cocoa%20carries%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20land%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20our%20job%20to%20bring%20that%20out%20with%20our%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20about%20working%20with%20them%20is%20the%20respect%20they%20have%20for%20our%20offering.%20They%20pay%20us%20above-market%20rates%20for%20our%20fruit%2C%20but%20more%20than%20that%2C%20we%20see%20the%20value%20of%20what%20we%20grow.%20When%20our%20cacao%20goes%20through%20their%20Fermentery%20with%20all%20the%20scientific%20fermentation%20and%20drying%20processes%20that%20they%20carry%20out%20and%20it%20is%20turned%20into%20fine%20flavour%20cacao%20beans%2C%20it%20gives%20us%20tremendous%20pride.%20We%20know%20exactly%20where%20our%20fruit%20is%20going%2C%20and%20we%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20made%20into%20something%20truly%20special.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20farmers%20here%20produced%20cocoa%20in%20a%20conventional%20method%2C%20Muppala%20faced%20another%20challenge%20related%20to%20the%20genetics%20of%20cocoa%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20history%20of%20its%20arrival%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-203x300.jpg%20203w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-768x1135.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-1039x1536.jpg%201039w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-1386x2048.jpg%201386w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-150x222.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465025%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Manam%20Chocolate%20Karkhana%2C%20processing%2C%20retailing%2C%20and%20crafting%20of%20chocolate%20are%20combined%20under%20a%20single%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20addressed%20the%20genetic%20problem%20through%20technological%20solutions%20developed%20by%20our%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Muppala%2C%20who%20noted%20that%20India%20grows%20only%200.5%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20cocoa.%20Even%20if%20the%20production%20were%20to%20increase%20fourfold%2C%20the%20output%20would%20only%20represent%202%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20cocoa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20area%20of%20land%20creates%20barriers%20to%20being%20a%20major%20player.%20The%20crop%20demands%20specific%20environmental%20conditions%2C%20including%20sufficient%20water%20and%20shade.%20It%20grows%20only%20between%2020%C2%B0%20north%20and%2020%C2%B0%20south%20of%20the%20Equator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20may%20never%20be%20a%20major%20cocoa-growing%20country%2C%20but%20we%20can%20make%20India%20a%20%E2%80%98premium%E2%80%99%20cocoa-growing%20nation.%20After%20having%20engaged%20over%20150%20farmers%20cultivating%20cocoa%20across%20a%20collective%20area%20of%203%2C000%20acres%20and%20making%20it%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20cocoa-growing%20region%2C%20we%20constructed%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20fine-flavour%20cocoa%20fermentary%20at%20Tadikalapudi%20in%20West%20Godavari%20on%20a%20four-acre%20land%20in%202021%2C%20where%20we%20execute%20fermentation%20and%20drying%20with%20our%20advanced%20scientific%20technique%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muppala%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20story%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20wanted%20to%20craft%20chocolate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20270%20people%20worked%20on%20this%20project%20over%20four%20years%2C%20culminating%20in%20its%20launch.%20Muppala%20realized%20he%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20wanted%20to%20craft%20chocolate%20but%20ended%20up%20making%20something%20else.%20What%20about%20chocolate%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20came%20back%20to%20Hyderabad%20and%20started%20structuring%20what%20chocolate%20can%20be%20and%20should%20be%20for%20India%20as%20well%20as%20from%20India%20for%20the%20world.%20It%E2%80%99s%20our%20social%20proclivity%20as%20Indians%20to%20gift%2C%20share%2C%20and%20consume%20sweets%2C%E2%80%9D%20mentions%20Muppala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuppala%20has%20invested%20significantly%20in%20the%20business%2C%20including%20creating%20the%20Manam%20Chocolate%20Karkhana%2C%20where%20the%20processing%2C%20retailing%2C%20and%20crafting%20of%20chocolate%20are%20combined%20under%20a%20single%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpanning%20an%20area%20of%2010%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20the%20Karkhana%20offers%20a%20chance%20to%20discover%2C%20explore%2C%20experience%2C%20and%20engage%20with%20cacao%20and%20chocolate%20in%20a%20dynamic%20and%20interactive%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F503-1_11zon-1751876739-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%