ompost%20significantly%20improves%20soil%20health%2C%20strengthens%20the%20trees%2C%20and%20keeps%20the%20roots%20active.%20We%20also%20apply%20coconut%20husk%20mulch%20around%20the%20base%20of%20each%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20it%20helps%20retain%20soil%20moisture%20and%20keeps%20the%20roots%20cool%20during%20hot%20weather.%20The%20result%20is%20better%20fruit%20size%2C%20more%20consistent%20pod%20quality%2C%20and%20overall%20healthier%20trees.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-500x342.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-500x342.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-300x205.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-768x525.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_4473-copy_11zon-1751876725-150x103.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F6_Dried-Cacao-Beans_-Distint-Origins-Cacao-Fermentery_West-Godavari-DistrictAP_-photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC